increaseAuthorization.t.sol
├── when the new authorization amount calculation overflows uint256
│  └── it should revert
└── when the new authorization amount calculation does not overflow uint256
   ├── when the sender is the zero address
   │  └── it should revert
   └── when the sender is not the zero address
      ├── when the funder is the zero address
      │  └── it should revert
      └── when the funder is not the zero address
         ├── it should increase the authorization
         └── it should emit an Authorize event
